Never had those gummies, so can't say if it's accurate to what profile it's aimed at - But I can say this ..&#xD;
It is a DAMN tasty strawberry gummy recipe! WF Strawberry Gummy Candy had been forgotten in my stash, but I am happy that I found it again. I was afraid the Swedish Gummy would be too prominent, but it just sits in the back and adds a bit of brightness to the strawberry. The small amount of INW Cactus also adds that bit of wetness, without being able to taste the actual flavoring - and then the Vanilla Swirl ties it all together nicely.&#xD;
Great recipe! - Mixing up my second batch now!&#xD;
&#xD;
UPDATE: I've started mixing this recipe with Swedish Gummy at 1% instead - This suits my personal taste better.
